Subject: [PATCH 1/2] notificationmgr: Add systemd service file

Since we don't like the webos-initscripts approach.

Signed-off-by: Herman van Hazendonk <github.com@herrie.org>
---
 files/systemd/notificationmgr.service | 32 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 32 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 files/systemd/notificationmgr.service

diff --git a/files/systemd/notificationmgr.service b/files/systemd/notificationmgr.service
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..716373b
--- /dev/null
+++ b/files/systemd/notificationmgr.service
